data.name: help_tooltip.ToolTip
data.value: This program shows, how couriers will travel "Next courier" allows you to switch between couriers Top label displays which courier is chosen "Next route" switches routes of courier Howering over tooltip will show you it's adress, number of package, that will be delivered, and approximate time of approach When howering over warehouse tooltip (Slobozhanska 32) will also show you, whe courier will leave and when return "Next step" button allows you to watch all steps of a route Curier moves from red tooltip to green one "Select source" allows you to select an .csv file to import packages Status bar in the bottom of the form will inform you about current app status and will show, if an error happened
